data.description: Welcome to 517 Sara Lane, this adorable 3 bed 1 bath home includes updated flooring throughout the home, new paint, large backyard and RV parking. Don't forget the greenhouse and beautiful water features. This home offers comfort and convenience for anyone. Conveniently located near parks, shopping and food, don't miss this excellent opportunity for your next home or investment property.
